casebody.data:
BARTLETT, Respondent, v. DOWD, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Daniel Bartlett against Thomas H. Dowd, as administrator, etc.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY,

No opinion. Motion to strike case from the calendar. Granted.
